data.meta_site_name: Paisley & Jade - Vintage & Specialty Rentals in Virginia, Washington, DC and North Carolina
data.text:
Give us all the sleek and chic modern vibes! We adore the simple vintage styling Madison and Stuart incorporated into their reception space on the gorgeous grounds of Upper Shirley Vineyards. They selected some of our most unique pieces of upholstered furniture to create a couple swanky lounge areas that boasted fabulous mid-century flair! Enjoy scrolling through he details of these vintage vignettes captured by the talented Molly Scott Photography!

A terrific trio! Our funky Wicklow Chairs boast a surprising shape and unique shade of green. We love their high backs and pretty wooden pegged legs! They pair perfectly in this seating area with our beautiful blue Barstow Chair!

Our classic mid-century modern Drexel end table brings this whole look together and provides a chic little resting spot for guest’s cocktails.

Moving to the patio area we have this lovely lounge area that combines organic neutral textures with lux velvet upholstery!

Our Caruso Rug and pair of Wicker Peacock Chairs bring in just the right touch of boho-chic and organic vibes! Our Navy Square Pillow ties in this accent chair beautifully with our gorgeous Billings Sofa.

Rounding out this chic reception look are our Gold & Glass Coffee Table, modern Madison Chairs and Mauve Square Pillows.

Congratulations Madison & Stuart! Thank you for letting us play a small part in your big day!

FEATURED VENORDS

IMAGES – Molly Scott Photography

VENUE – Upper Shirley Vineyards

PLANNING – The Wedding Rabbit
